# App Publish and IIS Deploy

## All Related Applications

| App | Source Path | AppId | DotNetDll | ApiPort | IIS Virtual Path |
|-----|------------|-------|-----------|---------|-----------------|
| **DedgeAuth** (auth server) | `C:\opt\src\DedgeAuth` | — | `DedgeAuth.Api.dll` | 8100 | `/DedgeAuth` |
| **DocView** | `C:\opt\src\DocView` | `DocView` | `DocView.dll` | 8282 | `/DocView` |
| **GenericLogHandler** | `C:\opt\src\GenericLogHandler` | `GenericLogHandler` | `GenericLogHandler.WebApi.dll` | 8110 | `/GenericLogHandler` |
| **ServerMonitorDashboard** | `C:\opt\src\ServerMonitor` | `ServerMonitorDashboard` | `ServerMonitorDashboard.dll` | 8998 | `/ServerMonitorDashboard` |
| **AutoDocJson** | `C:\opt\src\AutoDocJson` | `AutoDocJson` | `AutoDocJson.Web.dll` | 5280 | `/AutoDocJson` |
