## IIS Deploy: All Apps at Once

```powershell
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\WebSites\IIS-DeployApp\IIS-RedeployAll.ps1"
```

Phases: 1) UNINSTALL all apps, 2) `iisreset /restart`, 3) DEPLOY DefaultWebSite first then all apps alphabetically.

